refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
arraystringfalseiconv_get_encoding stringtype"all"
Retrieve internal configuration variables of iconv extension.

&reftitle.returnvalues;
Returns the current value of the internal configuration variable if successful&return.falseforfailure;.
If type is omitted or set to "all", iconv_get_encoding returns an array that stores all these variables.

  &reftitle.examples;



    iconv_get_encoding example


<pre>
<?php
iconv_set_encoding("internal_encoding", "UTF-8");
iconv_set_encoding("output_encoding", "ISO-8859-1");
var_dump(iconv_get_encoding('all'));
?>
</pre>


    &example.outputs;


Array
(
    [input_encoding] => ISO-8859-1
    [output_encoding] => ISO-8859-1
    [internal_encoding] => UTF-8
)
